  @prompt
    Create an enhanced "Image with text" section that supports 0-3 customizable mini-icons. Features needed: SVG/PNG upload support, multiple placement options (before/after heading, inline with bullets, corner overlays on image, margin accents), individual icon settings (size presets 12-32px plus custom, color/tint for SVG, opacity 60-100%, position with pixel offset, z-index layers, optional animations like float/pulse/fade-in), visibility toggles for desktop/mobile, accessibility support (decorative vs informative with proper aria-hidden and alt text), performance optimization (lazy loading, inline small SVGs), mobile responsive behavior (80% scaling, reduced motion support), and layout stability without content layout shift., ให้เนื้อหาอยู่ตรงกึ่งกลาง, ให้เนื้อหาทั้งหมดอยู่ตรงกลางของหน้า

{% enddoc %}
